settings.heading: Ordering & Payment
settings.row_content:
What payment methods can I use?

You can use Credit Card, Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Maestro, iDeal, or Paypal.

settings.heading: Shipping & Returns
settings.row_content:
To which countries do you deliver?

We offer Worldwide Shipping but only on the Home Accessories and Body & Beauty collections. Shipping costs will be calculated at checkout based on country of delivery.

What is the shipping cost?

Shipping costs will be calculated at checkout based on country of delivery.

We ship worldwide but at DAP conditions (duties and taxes not paid).

settings.heading: Scalar Science
settings.row_content:
Where can I find more product details?

More product details are available from the widget on product’s page.

These include, for example, technical specification, drawings, installation manuals and images.

What is my warranty?

Your warranty is 1 year. However, you can extend this by registering your product using The Button. For more details about The Button, please click here.

How long do LEDs last?

Lifespan of LEDs depends on the product. You can find this information in the product page widget.
